3.22	Burnt_by_the_Sun_2	Burnt by the Sun 2	Burnt by the Sun 2 . It is the sequel to Mikhalkov's 1994 film Burnt by the Sun, set in the Eastern Front of World War II. Burnt by the Sun 2 had the largest production budget ever seen in the Russian cinema ($55 mln), but it turned out to be Russia's biggest box office flop, and received negative reviews from critics both in Russia and abroad.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/1/19/Burnt_by_the_Sun_2.jpg/220px-Burnt_by_the_Sun_2.jpg
